      <abstract>
        <p>British pound falls to seven-year low against $US; graph (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>THE POUND FALLS. The British pound fell to a seven-year low after investors decided British interest rates would not change and shifted money out of the currency. The pound settled at $1.4194, down from $1.436 on Thursday.</p>
      </block>
